      "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <title>产品介绍页</title>\n  <style>\n    :root {\n      --primary-color: #2A7BE4;\n      --secondary-color: #F5A623;\n      --background-color: #FFFFFF;\n      --text-primary: #333333;\n    }\n    * {\n      margin: 0;\n      padding: 0;\n      box-sizing: border-box;\n    }\n    body {\n      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n      background-color: var(--background-color);\n      color: var(--text-primary);\n      line-height: 1.6;\n    }\n    header, section, footer {\n      padding: 40px 20px;\n      max-width: 1200px;\n      margin: auto;\n    }\n    .hero-banner {\n      text-align: center;\n      background-color: var(--primary-color);\n      color: #fff;\n      padding: 80px 20px;\n    }\n    .hero-banner h1 {\n      font-size: 2.5em;\n      margin-bottom: 20px;\n    }\n    .hero-banner p {\n      font-size: 1.2em;\n      margin-bottom: 30px;\n    }\n    .hero-banner button {\n      background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n      border: none;\n      padding: 15px 30px;\n      font-size: 1em;\n      color: #fff;\n      cursor: pointer;\n      border-radius: 4px;\n    }\n    .features-section h2,\n    .how-it-works h2,\n    .testimonials h2 {\n      font-size: 2em;\n      margin-bottom: 20px;\n      text-align: center;\n    }\n    .features-section ul {\n      list-style: none;\n      display: flex;\n      flex-wrap: wrap;\n      justify-content: center;\n      gap: 20px;\n    }\n    .features-section li {\n      background-color: #f9f9f9;\n      padding: 20px;\n      border-radius: 8px;\n      flex: 1 1 calc(25% - 40px);\n      min-width: 200px;\n      box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n      text-align: center;\n    }\n    .how-it-works .steps {\n      display: flex;\n      flex-direction: column;\n      gap: 20px;\n      max-width: 800px;\n      margin: auto;\n    }\n    .how-it-works .step {\n      background-color: #f9f9f9;\n      padding: 20px;\n      border-left: 4px solid var(--primary-color);\n      border-radius: 4px;\n    }\n    .testimonials .cards {\n      display: flex;\n      flex-wrap: wrap;\n      gap: 20px;\n      justify-content: center;\n    }\n    .testimonial-card {\n      background-color: #fff;\n      border: 1px solid #eee;\n      border-radius: 8px;\n      padding: 20px;\n      max-width: 300px;\n      box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n      text-align: center;\n    }\n    .testimonial-card img {\n      width: 60px;\n      height: 60px;\n      border-radius: 50%;\n      object-fit: cover;\n      margin-bottom: 15px;\n    }\n    footer {\n      background-color: var(--primary-color);\n      color: #fff;\n      text-align: center;\n    }\n    footer nav a {\n      color: #fff;\n      margin: 0 10px;\n      text-decoration: none;\n    }\n    footer p {\n      margin-top: 10px;\n      font-size: 0.9em;\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n  <section class=\"hero-banner\">\n    <h1>产品名称</h1>\n    <p>一句核心价值描述，突出产品的独特优势。</p>\n    <button>立即体验</button>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"features-section\">\n    <h2>功能亮点</h2>\n    <ul>\n      <li>功能要点一简述</li>\n      <li>功能要点二简述</li>\n      <li>功能要点三简述</li>\n      <li>功能要点四简述</li>\n    </ul>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"how-it-works\">\n    <h2>工作原理</h2>\n    <div class=\"steps\">\n      <div class=\"step\">步骤一：描述第一步的使用流程。</div>\n      <div class=\"step\">步骤二：描述第二步的使用流程。</div>\n      <div class=\"step\">步骤三：描述第三步的使用流程。</div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"testimonials\">\n    <h2>用户评价</h2>\n    <div class=\"cards\">\n      <div class=\"testimonial-card\">\n        <img src=\"avatar1.jpg\" alt=\"用户1\">\n        <p>这个产品真的改变了我的工作方式，非常高效。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"testimonial-card\">\n        <img src=\"avatar2.jpg\" alt=\"用户2\">\n        <p>易用且功能强大，非常推荐给同事们。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"testimonial-card\">\n        <img src=\"avatar3.jpg\" alt=\"用户3\">\n        <p>界面简洁，操作流畅，赞！</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <footer class=\"footer-site\">\n    <nav>\n      <a href=\"#\">关于我们</a>\n      <a href=\"#\">隐私政策</a>\n      <a href=\"#\">联系我们</a>\n    </nav>\n    <p>© 2024 公司名称 | ICP 备案号</p>\n  </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>"
    }
